cs.GT, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DS, cs.AI 

The paper deals with revenue optimization in second-price auctions with reserve, which is a problem in game theory and optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.GT (Game Theory and Mechanism Design). The paper also presents a learning-based approach to solve the problem, which involves analyzing the loss function and designing algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with online advertising and search engines, which are applications of information retrieval (cs.IR). The algorithms presented in the paper involve optimization techniques, which are related to data structures and algorithms (cs.DS). Finally, the paper also involves designing algorithms for solving the problem, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
